Best Buy Co Inc said it filed aregistration statement with the Securities and ExchangeCommission for a proposed offering of 30 mln dlrs ofsubordinated extendable notes.    Underwriters are led by Piper, Jaffray and Hopwood Inc.Financing is expected to be completed within 30 days, thecompany said.    Proceeds will be used to fund the company's plannedexpansion. Reuter&#3;